david copperfield is a 1935 american film released by metro-goldwyn-mayer based upon the charles dickens novel the personal history , adventures , experience , & observation of david copperfield the younger . a number of characters and incidents from the novel were omitted â€“ notably david 's time at salem house boarding school , although one character he met at salem house ( steerforth ) was retained for the film as a head boy at the school david attended after his aunt betsey trotwood gained custody of him . the story was adapted by hugh walpole from the dickens novel , and the film was directed by george cukor from a screenplay by howard estabrook and lenore j. coffee , who was not credited .